Chantal Lauby https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chantal_Lauby 0 Chantal Lauby (born 23 March 1948) is a French actress, film director, screenwriter, humorist and TV host. She is a member and founder of the group of comedians Les Nuls alongside Alain Chabat and Dominique Farrugia.
